This product includes software developed at vLLM Project (https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm),
originally released under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Modifications by Icertis Solutions:
- SAE (Sparse Autoencoder) feature extraction via custom pooling runner
- Expert routing capture via forward hooks on MoE gate modules
- MoE router logits capture alongside SAE features
- Dense payload return for SAE measurement
- Activation histogram logging
- Custom type support for MsgPack serialization
- Early-exit model truncation via sae_max_layer parameter

These modifications add SAE-based representation learning capabilities to the vLLM inference engine
for contract clause classification tasks.

Original source: https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm
